Package: rTwChannel
Type: Package
Title: Twitter channel stream analitics
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-09-07
Author: Alfonso Crisci <a.crisci@ibimet.cnr.it>, Valentina Grasso <v.grasso@ibimet.cnr.it>
Maintainer: Alfonso Crisci <a.crisci@ibimet.cnr.it>
Description: This package performs analitics on Twitter datastreams obtained by a structured query by using Twitter search/streaming API. The form of data are frames of data where significant elements of tweets are reported.
Imports: curl, qdap, qdapRegex, qdapTools, igraph, tm, sjPlot, sjmisc, XLConnect, xts, stringr,downloader
Suggests: wordcloud
License: GPL-2
NeedsCompilation: no

